page.title: 13An 11 Year Olds Day
page.content: At 7.00 I wake up I wash and get dressed. 7.30 I go downstairs and eat my breakfast. 8.00 I feed my rabbit, budgerigars and cat. 8.10 I go and practice the piano. 8.20 I get stuff ready for school. 8.30 I go to school from Leigh it is approximately 5 Km. I go in my Mums Ford Fiesta. 8.40 I arrive at school. 9.00-3.15 School. We do Maths, English Art, craft & poetry. When I get home I watch television and walk the dog, sometimes I go bellringing, then I go to bed. Our favourite programme is Home Sweet Home. Our hobbies are dancing, bellringing and detective work.
